Sensor Dust /!/ Anyone else experience a sensor dust issue. I have the 24-105 and 16-35 f4. The 16-35 always manages to get dust on the lens. I clean my gear after every shoot and normally a quick blast of air before I head out and I always seem to be battling the problem. 

Anyone has to clean their sensor before. How did you do it?
